title: Welcome to My Website
text:
Welcome to Medhat Farwati’s Website
Hi, I am Medhat Farwati, currently a CRSP student at Case Western Reserve University and a Cardiology Fellow at the Cleveland Clinic Main Campus.
The purpose of this website is to showcase data analyses for Project B as part of the CRSP 431 Class. In the future, this site will also host additional analyses, insights, and visualizations related to the field of cardiology and beyond.
Feel free to explore and follow along with the progress of the project. Stay tuned for updates!

About Me
